  <brief_title>A Study of PEGASYS (Peginterferon Alfa-2a (40KD)) in Combination With COPEGUS (Ribavirin) in Interferon-Naive Patients With Chronic Hepatitis C Infection (CHC).</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind Study of the Effect of PEGASYS and Ribavirin Combination Therapy on Viral Kinetics and Virologic Response in Interferon-na√Øve Patients With Chronic Hepatitis C Genotype 1 Infection</official_title>
